{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99106-my-brother-s-wheeeeelchair","title":"My Brother's Wheeeeelchair","description":"Meet Durva and Dhrubo. And Dhrubo's wheeeeelchair. Join the brother and sister as they explore parks, markets, and many other places and have lots of fun together, just like siblings do.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Salil  Chaturvedi"],"illustrators":["Tanvi Bhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99106-my-brother-s-wheeeeelchair"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495678/size3/30c9c6f01105d7fa1d9b37bd919d931f.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495678/size6/30c9c6f01105d7fa1d9b37bd919d931f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143561/size6/322551704391e1ba9a5a33ad229607cb.jpg","text":"Wheeeeeeeeeeee!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143562/size6/9477b93694a230063da25dfcddfef162.jpg","text":"Here’s me and my brother on his wheelchair.\nEveryone who sees us,\nSays we make a crazy pair.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143572/size6/8eb670f935dc92f5c0a7efc1f67480b0.jpg","text":"He has painted both the wheels,\nIn blues, yellows and maroons.\nAnd sometimes, just for fun,\nHe also ties balloons.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143564/size6/569e40d3336c86eb16cffd64e6bf8ca6.jpg","text":"My brother’s very smart,\nHe’s got plenty of brains.\nHe helps me across puddles,\nWhen it rains.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143565/size6/f9096ba4338e02c7014e8346e0cdad7c.jpg","text":"When we go to the park,\nIn the evening to play,\nHe uses a horn,\nSo people make way.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143566/size6/56ad4c24c6d6074365aff65d50e8bbd4.jpg","text":"Going to the market with him,\nIs such a treat.\nHe has a rear-view mirror,\nFor when we’re on the street.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143567/size6/e30877d0707515a4d8ae78baa4b1b131.jpg","text":"Sometimes he takes his chair\nInto a shallow stream.\nI give it a good splash.\nOh, how he does scream!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143568/size6/5705d2b981178d8360ad1cb77cb77f12.jpg","text":"When baba and aai take us\nTo the hills for a hike,\nHe puts on special wheels --\nLike a mountain bike!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143569/size6/29eb6c69d877f5eac8ca9a2b952bacdd.jpg","text":"All our friends wait,\nFor their turn to ride,\nIt feels so good,\nWith the arms out wide.\nHe goes so fast,\nHe is called the wheelchair champ.\nAnd now all our friends know...","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143570/size6/8ffa430eb4e8c46e4432db713925e792.jpg","text":"Their house must have a ramp!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143571/size6/6df7f11d090ce21b2a421f7677ebd17c.jpg","text":"12/12","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":179}}